AP1050.name: Soft Diffusion
AP1050.desc: Moderate diffusion. Softens hard edges and shadows. Good for CYC scallops.

AP1100.name: Hard Diffusion
AP1100.desc: Extreme diffusion. Lowers intensity of light. Good for softening very harsh edged light. Cloudy day look.

AP1150.name: Linear Diffusion

AP1200.name: Early Morning Frost
AP1200.desc: A good medium diffusion. Softens shutter cuts and harsh gobo edges in new generation. A good diffusion to use when AP1650 is too light.

AP1400.name: Weaved Diffusion
AP1400.desc: A very wide light diffusion. Still allows original beam of light to be visible. Good for distributing light into shade and softening gobos. Not susceptible to wind noise in outdoor applications.

AP1450.name: Light Weaved Diffusion
AP1450.desc: Half version of AP1400. A very wide light diffusion. Still allows original beam of light to be visible. Good for distributing light into shade and softening gobos. Not susceptible to wind noise in outdoor applications.

AP1500.name: Flat Diffusion
AP1500.desc: Medium diffusion. Softens hard edges. Similar to AP1450. Good for softening harsh shutter cuts.

AP1550.name: Textured Diffusion
AP1550.desc: Moderate diffusion. Considerable softening of shadows and edges. Original image still visible.

AP1600.name: White Diffusion
AP1600.desc: Most extreme diffusion. Yellows light output. Softens shadows considerably. Good for softening lines in skin.

AP1650.name: Light Textured Diffusion
AP1650.desc: Good for softening harsh shutter lines or gobos. A commonly used diffusion for softening edges on new generation ellipsoid.

AP1800.name: Red Diffusion
AP1800.desc: Diffused red primary for CYC washes. Softens fixture "scallops".

AP1900.name: Blue Diffusion
AP1900.desc: Diffused blue primary for CYC washes. Softens fixture "scallops".

AP1950.name: Green Diffusion
AP1950.desc: Diffused green primary for CYC washes. Softens fixture "scallops".

AP2000.name: Apollo Blue Full CTB

AP2180.name: Apollo Orange 1/8 CTO

AP2190.name: Apollo Orange 2x CTO

AP2220.name: Apollo Straw 1/2 CTS

AP2280.name: Apollo Straw 1/8 CTS
